p = 0.04. RT in Block 1 (500.95 ± 85.41 ms) was slower than the RTs in the rest of the blocks (between 474.68 ± 59.89 and 480.41 ± 66.77 ms), except for Block 3 (482.09 ± 64.17 ms). There was no group effect, F(2, 133) = 0.48, p = 0.62, ƞ 2
p = 0.01, nor an interaction, F(14, 931) = 0.72, p = 0.76, ƞ 2
p = 0.01.
